text: Pardubice is a city in the Czech Republic. Is a capital city of Pardubice region. In year 2024, have about 92.362 people live there. It is in the east of the historical region Bohemia. Dominik Hašek, a famous ice hockey goaltender, was born there. File:Kostel sv.
